metadata.name: #001 LOSTBOY CASSETTE ‘sleepless’
metadata.description:
Welcome to the first Edition of the LOSTBOY Cassettes and Vinyl. Every piece is a 1/1. Each “cassette” comes with one song while each vinyl comes with 4 full songs. Stems are included for the cassettes but not vinyls. Both limited tokens will grant you complete rights to the Art and Music of the NFT.

Claiming one of these tokens will grant you access to our Artist Experience. Together, we will distribute your track on all Streaming Platforms - market it through our playlists, and in return, you will earn royalties on all the streams generated from the track.
